#turn lights on if NOT day AND IF room occupied then wait 180 seconds before checking
loop:
lb r0 1076425094 Activate Maximum
seq r0 r0 0 #is it night?
lb r1 322782515 Activate Maximum
or r2 r0 r1 #if night or occupied then turn on lights
breqz r2 3 #if not day or not occupied then skip
sb 555215790 On r2
sleep 180
yield
j loop